      <abstract>
        <p>A new Schiff base ester, 3-hydroxy-4-[(phenylimino)methyl]phenyl 4-(hexadecanoyloxy)benzoate was synthesized and its IR, <sup>1</sup>H-NMR, <sup>13</sup>C-NMR and MS spectroscopic data are presented.</p>
      </abstract>
